      • convertFilterStringToRegexString

        public static String convertFilterStringToRegexString(String sFilter,
                                                      boolean bFilterFromTheStart,
                                                      boolean bMultiWord)
        Converts user given string into a regexp expression for filtering in tables.
        Parameters:
        sFilter - the user input. Simple space means 'OR'. ' vagy ', ' or ', ' oder ' means 'OR' too. ' s ', ' and ', ' und ' means 'AND'.
        bFilterFromTheStart - bFilterFromTheStart
        bMultiWord - bMultiWord
        Returns:
        the regular expression
